Interface INamedItemStorage<ITEM>

  • Type Parameters:
    ITEM -

    public interface INamedItemStorage<ITEM>
extends IFieldedItemStorage<ITEM>
    Stores items that have names and allows search on those names and the item fields via the super class.
    Author:
    dawood
